# CODEOWNERS — default reviewers for pull requests.
#
# GitHub requests a review from the matching owner automatically when a PR
# touches a path. The LAST matching pattern wins, so the per-directory rules
# below refine the global fallback. Everything is owned by the sole maintainer
# for now; split ownership out as the team grows.

# Global fallback — owns anything not matched by a more specific rule below.
* @hellobasitsiddiqui

# Per-surface ownership (mirrors the mono-repo directory map in README.md).
/backend/  @hellobasitsiddiqui
/web/      @hellobasitsiddiqui
/webview/  @hellobasitsiddiqui
/android/  @hellobasitsiddiqui
/infra/    @hellobasitsiddiqui
/docs/     @hellobasitsiddiqui
